---
import BaseLayout from "../../layout/BaseLayout.astro";
import HabitatOSCallout from "../../components/habitat-os-callout.astro";

const mailto = "mailto:hey@thefocus.ai?subject=Executive%20Reporting%20-%20Build%20%26%20Ship";
---

<BaseLayout
  pageTitle="AI-Powered Executive Reporting | TheFocus.AI"
  description="Your executives shouldn't wait for slides. We build AI systems that let leadership self-serve insights from connected data sources — real answers in seconds, not reformatted dashboards."
  category="capabilities"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="py-8 md:py-16">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-graphite border border-ink/15 px-2 py-1 rounded">L2 &rarr; L3</span>
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-petrol font-medium">Insight Engine</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold mb-6 text-ink leading-tight">
        Your executives shouldn't wait for slides
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-graphite leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Department heads spend hours pulling data from five dashboards, reformatting into slides, and presenting numbers that are already stale. The CEO still asks "but what does this mean?" You can skip all of that.
      </p>
      <a
        href={mailto}
        class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-petrol text-paper font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:bg-petrol/90 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200"
      >
        Discuss Your Reporting Needs &rarr;
      </a>
    </section>

    <!-- Video (disabled for now)
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <video
          autoplay
          muted
          playsinline
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          poster="/videos/offerings/executive-reporting.mp4#t=0.1"
        >
          <source src="/videos/offerings/executive-reporting.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        </video>
      </div>
    </section>
    -->

    <!-- The Pain -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-6 font-medium">The Problem</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">Sound familiar?</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Department heads spend 4-6 hours every week pulling numbers from multiple dashboards and reformatting them into slide decks nobody reads carefully.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">By the time the report reaches the leadership meeting, the data is a week old. Decisions are made on stale information.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">The CEO asks a follow-up question and the answer is "I'll get back to you" — triggering another round of data pulling that takes another day.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 rounded-xl bg-tint-warm/30">
          <span class="text-vermilion font-bold flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">&times;</span>
          <p class="text-graphite">Different departments use different definitions for the same metrics. Revenue numbers from Sales don't match Finance. Nobody trusts the dashboards.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- The Approach -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <div class="border-l-4 border-petrol bg-paper rounded-r-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-4 font-medium">Our Approach</h2>
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-4">How we fix this</h3>
        <div class="mb-4">
          <HabitatOSCallout variant="inline" />
        </div>
        <p class="text-graphite leading-relaxed mb-6">
          We build an executive-intelligence Habitat — a system that connects to your data sources, establishes canonical metric definitions, and lets leadership query the business in natural language. Instead of waiting for slides, executives ask questions and get traced, source-attributed answers in seconds. The system learns which questions matter and starts surfacing insights proactively.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">1</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Discover</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">We audit your reporting landscape — every dashboard, every spreadsheet, every manually assembled deck. We find where metric definitions diverge and where the real questions live.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">2</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Structure</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">Canonical metric definitions get established. Data sources get connected into a unified semantic layer. The "what does this mean?" question gets answered once and codified.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-petrol/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-sm font-mono font-bold text-petrol">3</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="font-bold text-ink mb-1">Build</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-graphite">A conversational intelligence layer where executives ask questions in plain language and get answers with sources. Proactive briefings surface what matters before anyone asks. Every answer traces back to specific data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Proof Points -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-petrol mb-6 font-medium">Proof</h2>
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-ink mb-8">We've done this before</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/case-study/distill" class="group block border border-ink/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-petrol/30 transition-all">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-petrol mb-2">500M+</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-2">tweets per day filtered into 5-minute briefings</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-graphite mb-3">Distill — AI-powered content intelligence across Twitter, YouTube, and podcasts. From information overload to curated executive-ready briefings.</p>
          <span class="text-petrol text-sm font-medium group-hover:underline">Read case study &rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/case-study/upperhand-ai" class="group block border border-ink/10 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-petrol/30 transition-all">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-petrol mb-2">78%</p>
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-ink mb-2">faster talent decisions</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-graphite mb-3">Upper Hand — executives self-serve insights that previously required analyst teams. Survey, social, and brand data unified into natural language queries.</p>
          <span class="text-petrol text-sm font-medium group-hover:underline">Read case study &rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Related Offerings -->
    <section class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-graphite/60 mb-4 font-medium">Related Offerings</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/offerings/monthly-close" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-ink/8 hover:border-petrol/30 hover:bg-tint-cool/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-ink group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors">Monthly Close</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-graphite">Stop the 10-day scramble</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-petrol/40 group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors flex-shrink-0">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
        <a href="/offerings/customer-onboarding" class="group flex items-center gap-3 p-4 rounded-xl border border-ink/8 hover:border-petrol/30 hover:bg-tint-cool/20 transition-all">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-ink group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors">Customer Onboarding</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-graphite">Formalize the cross-team handoff chain</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-petrol/40 group-hover:text-petrol transition-colors flex-shrink-0">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="border-t border-ink/10 pt-16 pb-8">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
        <span class="text-xs font-mono text-graphite border border-ink/15 px-2 py-1 rounded">Build & Ship</span>
        <span class="text-xs font-medium text-graphite">2-6 weeks</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4 text-ink">Ready to give your executives real-time answers?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-graphite mb-8 max-w-2xl">
        The conversation starts with understanding what questions your leadership actually asks — and where the answers currently come from.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a
          href={mailto}
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-petrol text-paper font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:bg-petrol/90 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 text-center"
        >
          Talk to a principal
        </a>
        <a
          href="/capabilities"
          class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border-2 border-ink/20 text-ink font-medium uppercase text-sm tracking-wider rounded-full hover:border-petrol hover:text-petrol hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all duration-200 text-center"
        >
          See the Full Framework
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
